Restricted Skins.desc: It has been laminated and filled with every neon color imaginable.
Restricted Skins.lore: "Roy G. Biv? Never heard of 'em."

Restricted Skins.title: P2000 | Obsidian
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to look like it was submerged in lava and is solidifying into obsidian as it cools.
Restricted Skins.lore: Giving the term "glass cannon" a whole new meaning

Restricted Skins.title: PP-Bizon | Embargo
Restricted Skins.desc: Pieced together from found items, it has a teal base and various 1950's Havana advertisements.
Restricted Skins.lore: ¡Chao pescao!

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Dual Berettas | Balance
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A red rose has been painted on either grip over a black base and silver filigree.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: MP5-SD | Acid Wash
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Prior to assembly its metallic blue topcoat was exposed to acid. It has been finished with brass hardware.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Black and blue and brass all over

Mil-Spec Skins.title: SCAR-20 | Torn
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray-painted with a randomized stripe pattern.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: R8 Revolver | Memento
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: The luxury of its ivory grip pairs well with the intricate metalwork on the frame, barrel, and cylinder.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: M249 | Warbird
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Originally blue with a yellow heat shield, age and use have taken their toll on its appearance.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: This old bird deserves a rest

Mil-Spec Skins.title: G3SG1 | Black Sand
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a tan and black military camo pattern.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: The Coalition Taskforce was winning, so Mikah turned to a more... aggressive approach

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Nova | Plume
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Custom painted brown feathers overlay a wooden receiver and stock.

Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted with black and silver metallic paints using a marbleizing medium, then candy coated in three colors.

Covert Skins.title: M4A4 | The Emperor
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using the Emperor tarot card as inspiration.
Covert Skins.lore: Lead with your head, even if it means ignoring your heart

Covert Skins.title: Five-SeveN | Angry Mob
Covert Skins.desc: A brightly colored paint job inspired by street art has been applied.
Covert Skins.lore: "Inside voices, please"

Classified Skins.title: AUG | Momentum
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with bright colors and forward facing arrows.

Classified Skins.title: XM1014 | Incinegator
Classified Skins.desc: A custom paint job resembling a gator spitting fire has been applied.

Classified Skins.title: R8 Revolver | Skull Crusher
Classified Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with yellow flames and red and white accents.

Restricted Skins.title: AWP | Atheris
Restricted Skins.desc: A striking green and blue bush viper has been hand painted over a black base.
Restricted Skins.lore: As deadly as it is beautiful

Restricted Skins.title: Desert Eagle | Light Rail
Restricted Skins.desc: Its custom paint job creates an optical illusion and appears to change the weapon's geometry.
Restricted Skins.lore: Required power supply sold separately

Restricted Skins.title: UMP-45 | Moonrise
Restricted Skins.desc: A randomized city landscape in the foreground gives way to a full moon and purple-red night sky.
Restricted Skins.lore: Look for the North Star

Restricted Skins.title: Tec-9 | Bamboozle
Restricted Skins.desc: A custom bamboo paint job has been applied.
Restricted Skins.lore: Don't be deceived

Restricted Skins.title: MP5-SD | Gauss
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to look like it was assembled from pieces of stamped steel.
Restricted Skins.lore: Lovingly referred to as the "SpaceGat 2000"

Mil-Spec Skins.title: AK-47 | Uncharted
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A custom paint job of various tribal patterns has been applied.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: P250 | Verdigris
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: The green drips are the result of its copper base being exposed to the elements.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: P90 | Off World
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with multiple coats of blue paint; even more than last time.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: FAMAS | Crypsis
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray painted with a randomized insect pattern in autumn colors.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: MAC-10 | Whitefish
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Fish scales, bones, and hooks have been hand painted in white over a black base.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Galil AR | Akoben
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A rust-colored pattern has been spray painted over a white base.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: MP7 | Mischief
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A concerning black and white smile has been painted atop a red base.

Rare Special Items.title: Navaja Knife | Fade
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Rare Special Items.title: Navaja Knife | Crimson Web
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread

Rare Special Items.title: Navaja Knife | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted in a zebra-stripe pattern with aluminum and chrome paints with various reflectivities, and has then been covered with a tomato red candy coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Valeria doesn't pay Javier to ask questions... she pays him to pry out answers

Rare Special Items.title: Navaja Knife | Case Hardened
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.
Rare Special Items.lore: A little color never hurt anyone

Rare Special Items.title: Navaja Knife | Blue Steel
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been cold blued.
Rare Special Items.lore: This is the malbec of weapon design - Booth, Arms Dealer

Rare Special Items.title: Navaja Knife | Stained
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been given a forced patina using lemon and mustard dripped onto the surface.
Rare Special Items.lore: If you think it's messy now, wait until you see it under a blacklight

Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil.

Classified Skins.lore: Same technology, now available in a smaller form factor

Restricted Skins.desc: A bright orange pattern of skeletal birds has been applied.

Restricted Skins.desc: A hydrographic pattern of red hexagons has been applied over a dark blue base.
Restricted Skins.lore: Information is never free

Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to appear as if it is filled with red tubes.

Rare Special Items.lore: A must have for any demolitions expert with sweaty palms

Rare Special Items.title: Sport Gloves | Superconductor
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. The blue and black gloves are ideal for those who wish to be phenomenal.
Rare Special Items.lore: They don't want none

Rare Special Items.title: Sport Gloves | Hedge Maze
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. The green and white gloves were manufactured by Icarus Athletics.
Rare Special Items.lore: Only cowards fear flying close to the sun

Rare Special Items.title: Sport Gloves | Arid
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. Multiple shades of brown and a subtle camo print give these gloves a distinguished look.
Rare Special Items.lore: If we're going to be heroes, we may as well look the part... - Rona Sabri, Rising Star

Covert Skins.title: M4A4 | Buzz Kill
Covert Skins.desc: This Sektor Industry firearm has been sleekly painted in yellow and green.
Covert Skins.lore: There's one at every party

Covert Skins.title: SSG 08 | Dragonfire
Covert Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of a monstrous dragon snorting fire.
Covert Skins.lore: Sit on your horde and wait for any who come to take it

Classified Skins.title: Sawed-Off | Wasteland Princess
Classified Skins.desc: Someone has been keeping track of kills on the barrel.
Classified Skins.lore: A perfect gift for the sociopath that has everything...

Rare Special Items.title: M9 Bayonet | Doppler
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted with black and silver metallic paints using a marbleizing medium, then candy coated.
Rare Special Items.lore: Getting lost in its color can prove fatal

Rare Special Items.title: M9 Bayonet | Tiger Tooth
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been anodized orange and hand-etched in a tiger stripe pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: Like the tiger it is rare... like the tiger it is deadly...

Rare Special Items.title: M9 Bayonet | Damascus Steel
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been forged from a billet made from two different types of carbon steel.
Rare Special Items.lore: Finally, a weapon strong enough to match your resolve

Rare Special Items.desc: It is still perfectly operational although the exterior surfaces have rusted.
Rare Special Items.lore: Some people don't need to hide how dirty their deeds are

Rare Special Items.title: M9 Bayonet | Ultraviolet
Rare Special Items.desc: It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a black and purple color scheme.
Rare Special Items.lore: Elegant design paired with brutal intent

Covert Skins.desc: It has been hand painted in vibrant colors and accentuated by a smiley face on the stock.
Covert Skins.lore: Protect what is yours

Covert Skins.title: PP-Bizon | Judgement of Anubis
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in an Egyptian theme.
Covert Skins.lore: Its trigger weighs lighter than a feather

Classified Skins.title: P250 | Asiimov
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design.
Classified Skins.lore: If you think I need a rifle to kill a man, you have no idea who you're talking to... - Mikha Biton, Phoenix Sniper

Classified Skins.title: AUG | Fleet Flock
Classified Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of birds flying through clouds.
Classified Skins.lore: Some birds represent harmony and peace... these are not those birds

Classified Skins.title: UMP-45 | Primal Saber
Classified Skins.desc: It has been given a decal of a sabertooth tiger skull
Classified Skins.lore: Every predator eventually meets their end

Restricted Skins.title: SSG 08 | Ghost Crusader
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted white and given arctic blue accents.
Restricted Skins.lore: I can never replace what was taken from us... but I can take even more from them - The Phoenix and The Initiate Part 2

Restricted Skins.title: XM1014 | Black Tie
Restricted Skins.desc: A vision in black and white chrome, this shotgun is best used on formal occasions.
Restricted Skins.lore: We have Izaki and Cocinero. You need them for anything or can I just kill them now? - The Mercenary and The Serpent Part 1

Restricted Skins.title: Galil AR | Firefight
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been given crimson accents and a hand painted icon.
Restricted Skins.lore: Booth had this weapon commissioned for Valeria in an attempt to smooth things over with the Phoenix

Restricted Skins.title: CZ75-Auto | Red Astor
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with red and white accents.
Restricted Skins.lore: Booth has become synonymous with family drama; and who has time for drama when we're talking business - Huxley, The Competition

Restricted Skins.title: Tec-9 | Re-Entry
Restricted Skins.desc: The barrel has been given a flame decal.
Restricted Skins.lore: I hate being right all the time - Carmen Cocinero, Extraction Expert

Mil-Spec Skins.title: MP9 | Bioleak
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Varying shades of green create the illusion of a chemical spill.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: SG 553 | Atlas

Mil-Spec Skins.title: P2000 | Oceanic

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Has anyone heard from Kotaro or Carmen? - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Dual Berettas | Ventilators

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: A weapon for artists, by artists

Mil-Spec Skins.title: M249 | Spectre

Rare Special Items.title: M9 Bayonet | Rust Coat
Rare Special Items.desc: It is still perfectly operational although the exterior surfaces have rusted.
Rare Special Items.lore: Some people don't need to hide how dirty their deeds are

Rare Special Items.title: M9 Bayonet | Ultraviolet
Rare Special Items.desc: It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a black and purple color scheme.
Rare Special Items.lore: Elegant design paired with brutal intent

Covert Skins.title: Galil AR | Chatterbox
Covert Skins.desc: It has been hand-painted and distressed. The skull painted over the dust cover appears to chatter when the bolt reciprocates.
Covert Skins.lore: Some say that when you laugh, the world laughs with you...but when Chatterbox laughs there are only screams

Covert Skins.title: AWP | Man-o'-war
Covert Skins.desc: It has been given a base coat of blue metallic paint then hand-painted with metallic gold swirls and accents.
Covert Skins.lore: Turn some heads before you take them off

Classified Skins.title: M4A4 | 龍王 (Dragon King)
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a dragon in red and blue.
Classified Skins.lore: A weapon worthy of The Monkey King himself - Booth, Arms Dealer

Classified Skins.title: AK-47 | Cartel
Classified Skins.desc: It has been engraved with skeletons, flowers and serpents.
Classified Skins.lore: One little squeeze turns every morning into the Day of the Dead

Classified Skins.title: P250 | Muertos
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with circular motifs.
Classified Skins.lore: This one is steeped in tradition and blood

Restricted Skins.title: Desert Eagle | Naga
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been engraved with a mythological motif.
Restricted Skins.lore: A beast in Indian mythology as well as on the battlefield

Restricted Skins.title: MAC-10 | Malachite
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted using metallic effect paints and given a wavy pattern using a rubber comb tool.
Restricted Skins.lore: Bright colors hide a gun with a dark purpose

Restricted Skins.title: Dual Berettas | Urban Shock
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with urban camo and blue accents.
Restricted Skins.lore: With lightning always comes thunder

Restricted Skins.title: Sawed-Off | Serenity
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with the image of a woman with wings.
Restricted Skins.lore: Serenity is a luxury few can afford - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary

Mil-Spec Skins.title: MP9 | Deadly Poison
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with dynamic, angular shapes and a stylized spider.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It's not the first bite that kills you, it's the 29 that come after

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Glock-18 | Catacombs
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a hydrographic of skulls over a silver metallic paint base.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Intimidation is the sincerest form of flattery

Mil-Spec Skins.title: M249 | System Lock
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: SCAR-20 | Grotto
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been sponged and brush-painted with blue metallic effect paints.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: The founder of Season Corporation had this piece commissioned after being rescued by renowned Operator Kotaro Izaki

Mil-Spec Skins.title: XM1014 | Quicksilver
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a translucent hydrographic with a terrain map motif over metallic silver paint.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Sometimes you need an unstable element to solve your problems - Kotaro Izaki, Breach Expert

Covert Skins.lore: One day they will ask why we fight, and when they do they will understand - Naomi, Bodyguard to Valeria Jenner

Covert Skins.title: P2000 | Fire Elemental
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a creature made of fire in a graphic style.
Covert Skins.lore: Sometimes playing with fire is a good thing

Classified Skins.title: XM1014 | Tranquility
Classified Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with the image of a woman with long hair.
Classified Skins.lore: I'm not here for what I need; I'm here for something I want - Imogen and The Oni Part 2

Classified Skins.title: SCAR-20 | Cardiac
Classified Skins.desc: It has been heat wrapped with vinyl pre-printed in a modern orange and blue design.

Classified Skins.title: P250 | Cartel
Classified Skins.desc: It has been engraved with skeletons, flowers and serpents.
Classified Skins.lore: One little squeeze turns every morning into the Day of the Dead

Restricted Skins.title: M4A4 | Griffin
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand-painted with an illustration of a griffin.
Restricted Skins.lore: Felix handpicked his team from operators all over the world... and while people question their personalities, they never question the results

Restricted Skins.title: M4A1-S | Basilisk
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been etched with a basilisk.
Restricted Skins.lore: It's rude to stare, but war isn't the time for pleasantries

Restricted Skins.title: Glock-18 | Grinder
Restricted Skins.desc: The steel slide has been painted using a combination of stenciling and hand-painting using oil paints.
Restricted Skins.lore: The only way to make diamonds is by applying pressure

Restricted Skins.title: Sawed-Off | Highwayman
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been lacquered in black and gold using a scotch thistle motif.
Restricted Skins.lore: You don't have to hold your pinky out when pulling the trigger, but it's a nice touch

Mil-Spec Skins.title: MAG-7 | Firestarter
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray-painted in layers then distressed to give the appearance of burning edges.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It always begins with a tiny spark

Mil-Spec Skins.title: UMP-45 | Delusion
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been screen printed with a nautilus design.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Five-SeveN | Urban Hazard
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with urban camo and red accents.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Every year, Booth gathers the worlds foremost designer gunsmiths to show off their latest designs

Mil-Spec Skins.title: MP9 | Dart
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a striped hydrographic arranged in a chevron pattern.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Throw enough downfield and you're bound to hit the bullseye eventually

Mil-Spec Skins.title: G3SG1 | Murky
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been anodized then painted using a leopard-spot hydrographic.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: There is always some place darker you can go
